root.description: The NFT Raffle Smart Contract is designed to facilitate a raffle system where participants can enter by purchasing tickets using cryptocurrency. Winners are selected at random, and the prize is an NFT (Non-Fungible Token). This project leverages blockchain technology to ensure transparency, fairness, and security in the raffle process.
root.name: nft-raffle
